products.title: Meadow Nightingale Blue 89mm Vertical Blind
products.description: White on blue creates such a striking and classic contrast that helps to make this stylish window blind really pop. The meadow nightingale vertical blind features a pollergen treated fabric with a gorgeous design of wild flowers. This window blind is a smart and decorative way to bring peaceful shading to any family space. Product id: db-vtb1429 fabric colour: nightingale blue material: 100% polyester headrail: white slimline headrail supported by white steel brackets - top or face fixable slat width: 89mm control type: smooth chain operation with cord tilt or wand tilt and pull energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - effective thermal retention light filtering: yes meadow nightingale blue 89mm vertical blind in blue.
